                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il fait nuit noire au fond de l'antre,\nOù nul rayon ne vient fleurir,\nEt c'est là, couché sur son ventre,\nQue le grand Lion va mourir."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Sa longue chevelure pâle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "S'affaisse sur son corps tremblant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Et voici déjà que le râle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Sort de sa poitrine, en sifflant.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sa longue chevelure pâle\nS'affaisse sur son corps tremblant,\nEt voici déjà que le râle\nSort de sa poitrine, en sifflant."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Or le Renard, plein de génie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Vient, ainsi qu'un lâche irrité,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Insulter à cette agonie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Avec un cynisme effronté.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Or le Renard, plein de génie,\nVient, ainsi qu'un lâche irrité,\nInsulter à cette agonie\nAvec un cynisme effronté."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Il dit au Lion : — Pauvre Sire !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "La vie heureuse et libre fuit",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Ton front plus blême que la cire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Et tu vas rouler dans la nuit !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il dit au Lion : — Pauvre Sire !\nLa vie heureuse et libre fuit\nTon front plus blême que la cire,\nEt tu vas rouler dans la nuit !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Dans ta prunelle douloureuse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Que jadis caressait l'air pur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Tu n'auras plus que l'ombre affreuse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Sans astre, ni plafond d'azur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dans ta prunelle douloureuse\nQue jadis caressait l'air pur,\nTu n'auras plus que l'ombre affreuse,\nSans astre, ni plafond d'azur."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Tu subiras l'éternel jeûne",
